name: @ionic-native/nfc
readme: Improve this doc # UriHelper onic cordova plugin add phonegap-nfc $ npm install --save @ionic-native/nfc ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/nfc/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/chariotsolutions/phonegap-nfc](https://github.com/chariotsolutions/phonegap-nfc) The NFC plugin allows you to read and write NFC tags. You can also beam to, and receive from, other NFC enabled devices. Use to - read data from NFC tags - write data to NFC tags - send data to other NFC enabled devices - receive data from NFC devices This plugin uses NDEF (NFC Data Exchange Format) for maximum compatibilty between NFC devices, tag types, and operating systems. ## Supported platforms - Android - BlackBerry 10 - Windows - Windows Phone 8
